             was indicted for <rs id="t18281204-204-off1086" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18281204-204-off1086" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18281204-204-off1086" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18281204-204-cd1087" type="crimeDate">24th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281204-204-off1086 t18281204-204-cd1087"></join>, 3 tables, value 7s.; 3 pieces of carpet, value 1s. 6d,, and 1 pieces of oil-cloth, value 1s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18281204-204-victim1728" type="victimName">
                  Frances 
                  Taylor
               <interp inst="t18281204-204-victim1728" type="surname" value="Taylor"></interp>
